{"tid":747350,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"你身邊有幾多個電腦白痴？","createTime":"2018-07-18T10:04:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-20T08:22:51.000Z","uid":23094,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"7febde8e1c7386d3a5be80d802b5a0005a1b23bc","tid":747350,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T10:04:49.000Z","msg":"一個以為OS即係Windows<br />\n叫佢買Mac機，有咩事打個電話就有專人教你點做<br />\n佢：係咪有埋Windows，唔使自己裝？<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一個以為複製軟件就等於翻版<br />\n唔理解軟件還軟件，Key還Key<br />\n我話燒隻Windows ISO落碟畀佢裝，叫佢自己揾Key<br />\n佢：咁咪即係翻版？<br />\n我：咁你條Key係正版嘛<br />\n佢：但係隻碟係翻版㗎喎<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71a048a4308a7ac4aa393e5bdf23ad146df39325","tid":747350,"uid":189053,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T10:07:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2b4d0cb377d651258bd688e2737f35e9eb975a0e","tid":747350,"uid":67413,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T10:11:09.000Z","msg":"原來window要買㗎？唔係砌完機一開就有㗎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6318f96ad4d29afd01a2e34f2239bbbdb5041eec","tid":747350,"uid":127466,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T10:18:31.000Z","msg":"佢話部 Notebook 攪左成半鐘都上唔到網,  跟住我睇番自己手機 wifi 又連到線. 跟住再望下佢部 notebook, 原來有個 wifi 實體掣, 佢無意間 off 左.  佢話 : 吓, 原來自己部腦 wifi 有掣 on/off <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d4d6f15e14395a34a86235541c3458a8f83b387","tid":747350,"uid":1402,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T10:18:52.000Z","msg":"樓豬=電腦白痴 <img src=\"https://ohw.ooo/husky/huskyloli.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fohw.ooo%2Fhusky%2Fhuskyloli.gif&h=7c75a63c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"71b90f6f32a5fc75a040c41aa62cc34179d64723","tid":747350,"uid"