>\n<br />\n問我：window要買㗎咩？乜唔係一砌完部機就有？"},{"pid":"9a3ba253a3ece89ec258b4eee8ed7ed6f0843ddc","tid":747350,"uid":10009,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"7aaa42c43159d2f2814b4c2d9d93379032fdfa1d","tid":747350,"uid":23094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5ca9f457b912199ead89c75f047703d0ece17260","tid":747350,"uid":10009,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"8a30aa334ba63ef170d78357fa13642b4b0ea827","tid":747350,"uid":1085,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T16:12:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T16:38:44.000Z","msg":"呢啲唔係電腦白痴 係on99 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T16:54:14.000Z","msg":"唔好喺度引罵戰騎劫個Post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T17:19:01.000Z","msg":"邊個唔同意 邊個就係on9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw 呢個世界好多人拎住「電腦白痴」做盾牌然後就會問你一啲真係白鳩痴既問題<br />\n「唔好意思 你當我電腦白痴 點解XXXXXXXX既?」<br />\n拎住「電腦白痴」就可以不經大腦不假思索咁問你問題，相比起直接問你一個白痴問題既人，呢啲人更為討厭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb48b57af29b0a83e00b3e6c13335c671b29d24c","tid":747350,"uid":23094,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T17:59:13.000Z","msg":"以為影片檔案越大代表越高畫質<br />\n唔知有編碼同解析度呢回事<br />\n佢：嗰個得幾百MB，呢個差唔多成GB，梗係留呢個啦<br />\n我：成GB嗰個avi嚟，幾百MB嗰個係mp4，解析度仲要高啲喎<br />\n佢：但係咁細，一定好低清啦<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"737772d63c5556a87be61435d7b49ae2bb32b928","tid":747350,"uid":1402,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T19:52:55.000Z","msg":"NysKing #116953: [HKUG] 高登＋連登 ＝ 聯登........略<br />\n十二歲信奉馬克思#183302: 想食兩家茶禮 食屎喇你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc7bebb8c9ec17e2dba93e28e95d1f5129c3bf56","tid":747350,"uid":45001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T20